name: E X T R A V A G A N Z A

metadata.name: BLACK AND RED EXTRAVAGANZA
metadata.description: A fashion model wearing a black and red dress is making a bold and striking impression on the audience. She looks confident and poised as she struts down the runway. All eyes are on her glamorous dress and her beauty. She’s a true professional, her perfect appearance disguises her true emotions. Her stare is lost in thought, it’s just another show.
